OL,3,CAgency staff join striking bin workers
OL,4,Camid claims of bullying and harassment
OL,6,FAgency workers have joined striking
OL,7,Fbin workers on picket lines in the
OL,8,Fcity centre over claims of "bullying
OL,9,Fand harassment at the council's refuse
OL,10,Fdepartment two weeks ago."
OL,12,FA rally was held by Unite The Union at
OL,13,FSmithfield Depot on Pershore Street,
OL,14,FBirmingham, on Monday morning 1
OL,15,FDecember) to mark the first day of
OL,16,Fstrike action by agency refuse workers.
