OL,3,CAgency staff join striking bin workers
OL,4,Camid claims of bullying and harassment
OL,6,FUnite said the Job & Talent agency
OL,7,Fworkers had voted in favour of strike
OL,8,Faction to join the picket along with
OL,9,Fbin workers from Birmingham city
OL,10,Fcouncil.
OL,12,FThe agency workers have been carrying
OL,13,Fout bin collections during
OL,14,FBirmingham's long running bin strike,
OL,15,Fwhich have been ongoing since January.
OL,17,FThe industrial action could continue
OL,18,Fbeyond May's local elections. The
OL,19,Fdirectly-employed bin workers voted in
OL,20,Ffavour of extending their industrial
OL,21,Faction mandate in November.
