OL,3,CAgency staff join striking bin workers
OL,4,Camid claims of bullying and harassment
OL,6,FUnite the Union says the number of
OL,7,Fagency workers who are willing to join
OL,8,Fthe strike action is "growing daily".
OL,10,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,11,Fsaid: "Birmingham council will only
OL,12,Fresolve this dispute when it stops the
OL,13,Fappalling treatment of its workforce.
OL,15,F"Agency workers have now joined with
OL,16,Fdirectly-employed staff to stand up
OL,17,Fagainst the massive injustices done to
OL,18,Fthem.
