OL,6,F"Instead of wasting millions more of
OL,7,Fcouncil taxpayers' money fighting a
OL,8,Fdispute it could settle justly for a
OL,9,Ffraction of the cost, the council
OL,10,Fneeds to return to talks with Unite
OL,11,Fand put forward a fair deal for all
OL,12,Fbin workers.
OL,14,F"Strikes will not end until it does."
OL,16,FTwo agency workers, Luke and Andy
OL,17,FGraham told ITV News Central 'it's not
OL,18,Fright the way they are being treated'
