OL,3,CAgency staff join striking bin workers
OL,4,Camid claims of bullying and harassment
OL,6,FBirmingham city council said: "While
OL,7,Fwe are disappointed the dispute has
OL,8,Fnot been resolved as Unite has
OL,9,Frejected all our offers, we are
OL,10,Fcontinuing to make regular waste
OL,11,Fcollections and our contingency plan
OL,12,Fis working.
OL,14,F"We have been collecting an average of
OL,15,Fapproximately 1,330 tonnes of kerbside
OL,16,Fwaste every day, more than we did
OL,17,Fprior to industrial action, and over
OL,18,Fthe last six months we have collected
OL,19,Fover 100,000 tonnes of kerbside waste.
