OL,6,F"There has been a 22 per cent increase
OL,7,Fin tonnage of waste collected per
OL,8,Femployee and a 52 per cent improvement
OL,9,Fregarding missed collections.
OL,11,F"A small number of agency staff are in
OL,12,Fa separate dispute with Job & Talent.
OL,13,FThe city council has contingency plans
OL,14,Fand will continue to look to maintain
OL,15,Fresidents with a minimum of one
OL,16,Fcollection a week.
OL,18,F"Meanwhile we continue to move forward
OL,19,Fwith the service improvements that are
OL,20,Flong overdue and that our residents
OL,21,Fneed."
